    desc: "Seasonal demand is predictable. Seasonal inventory problems are not inevitable  they are the result of predictable demand being met with reactive planning. The brand that plans its Diwali inventory in October is already too late. The brand that planned it in August has the right stock, in the right channels, at the right cost.",
