    desc: "Every decision that is made one week late has a one-week cost. At ₹15,000 daily marketing spend, a one-week delay in pausing a failing campaign costs ₹105,000. At ₹4 lakh monthly revenue per SKU, a one-week delay in placing a reorder costs ₹1 lakh in stockout revenue. Delayed decisions are not free. They have a precisely calculable daily cost.",
