    desc: "The KPIs that matter at ₹5 lakh monthly revenue are not the same as the ones that matter at ₹50 lakh. Tracking the same metrics across all growth stages produces a business that is optimising for yesterday's priorities while the current stage's critical variables go unmonitored.",
