    title: "How Shipping Delays Impact Lifetime Value (LTV)",
    desc: "The shipping delay that costs ₹0 in direct charges costs ₹1,200 in LTV when the delayed delivery is a customer's first order. The customer who waited seven days for a product promised in three does not consciously think 'I will not come back.' They simply do not come back  and the LTV that should have been ₹2,400 over three years is ₹799 for one order.",
