    desc: "Checking daily metrics that should be checked weekly wastes cognitive capacity and produces anxiety without action. Missing weekly metrics that should be checked daily allows preventable problems to compound for seven days. The right monitoring frequency for each metric is not a preference  it is a function of how quickly the metric changes and how quickly the decision it informs must be made.",
