    title: "Delivery Speed vs Delivery Accuracy: What Matters More",
    desc: "The brand that delivers in 2 days but sends the wrong product 4% of the time is creating more customer damage than the brand that delivers in 4 days and sends the right product 99.5% of the time. Speed and accuracy are both important  but when forced to choose, accuracy determines repeat purchase and speed determines acquisition.",
