    desc: "The business earning 18% net margin at ₹20 lakh monthly revenue that earns 8% net margin at ₹70 lakh monthly revenue has not become less efficient. It has allowed a set of costs to scale faster than its gross margin  and the fix is specific, actionable, and almost always possible without slowing the growth.",
