    title: "Enterprise AI Is Broken: Why It's Not Delivering ROI",
    desc: "Billions have been spent on AI across enterprises worldwide, yet manual follow-ups still dominate daily operations. Dashboards multiply, pilots launch, and most quietly die. The missing layer is not intelligence  it is execution.",
