          "The execution layer is not a dashboard. It is not an alert. It is an autonomous system that owns the workflow from signal to resolution, acts across integrated systems, and surfaces only genuine exceptions for human review. The enterprise AI stack is not broken at the intelligence layer. It is broken because the execution layer does not exist.",
