    title:
      "The Core Problem: AI Gives Insights, But Enterprises Need Execution",
    desc: "LLMs can summarise, forecast, and flag anomalies with impressive accuracy. What they cannot do is close the loop. The gap between an AI-generated insight and a resolved enterprise workflow is where most AI value is lost  and it is a structural gap, not a technology gap.",
