          "Each AI dashboard added to an enterprise workflow creates three categories of cognitive load: the load of reviewing the dashboard's outputs, the load of determining which outputs require action and which are noise, and the load of coordinating with other teams to execute on the outputs that do require action. The first two loads were anticipated. The third load  which scales with the number of tools and the number of cross-team dependencies  was not.",
