          "Building an enterprise execution system on top of an LLM without addressing these architectural gaps is equivalent to building a logistics operation around a system that is excellent at generating shipping labels but has no mechanism for tracking whether the shipment was picked up, is in transit, or has been delivered. The intelligence layer works. The execution architecture is absent.",
