    desc: "Every channel has its own dashboard, its own inventory requirements, its own settlement cycle, and its own customer expectations. The brand managing three channels from a shared spreadsheet is not running a multi-channel business. It is running three separate businesses with a common bank account  and the coordination failures between them are costing lakhs per month.",
    author: "Manroze",
