    title: "Small Manufacturing Units: Why They Struggle to Scale",
    desc: "India has 63 million MSMEs. Most manufacturing units in this segment produce good products, have genuine demand, and still cannot grow beyond a certain size. The ceiling is almost never the product. It is the planning, the data, and the systems that the product sits inside.",
