    desc: "The hustle that built the business to ₹30 lakh monthly revenue will not build it to ₹1 crore. Not because the hustle was wrong  it was exactly right. But because the capability that the next phase requires is not more effort. It is a fundamentally different way of operating.",
    author: "Prince Kumar",
