          "Total manual process time: approximately 25 to 35 hours per week across the team  the equivalent of a full-time employee dedicated entirely to maintaining manual processes. At ₹20,000 to ₹30,000 per month for that employee's equivalent labour cost, the manual process overhead is costing the business ₹2.4 to ₹3.6 lakh annually in direct labour  before accounting for the errors, delays, and missed decisions that the manual processes generate.",
