          "The specific value of real-time operational data is not the data itself. It is the decisions that current data enables that stale data prevents. A founder who knows by 9am that yesterday's primary campaign delivered CAC above threshold can pause it before the morning spend cycle begins. A founder who discovers the same fact in the weekly review has already spent five to seven days of excess spend. The decision speed advantage described in article 10 requires current data as its foundation  and manual processes fundamentally cannot produce current data.",
