    text: "Inventory Dead Stock: The ₹10L Mistake Most Founders Ignore",
    title: "Inventory Dead Stock: The ₹10L Mistake Most Founders Ignore",
    desc: "The ₹10 lakh sitting in your warehouse as slow or dead stock is not an asset. It is a liability that is costing you ₹23 lakh per year to hold, blocking the working capital that would fund your next growth phase, and slowly writing itself off while you focus on acquiring new customers.",
    author: "Manroze",
