    text: "3 AI Skills That Can Make You ₹1 Lakh/Month",
    title: "3 AI Skills That Can Make You ₹1 Lakh/Month",
    desc: "These are not theoretical skills. They are skills that working professionals and freelancers in India are monetising right now  in 2026  at ₹1 lakh per month and above. Here is what they are, why they pay, and how to build them.",
