    desc: "Revenue without gross margin is not a business. It is a transaction volume problem. The founders who build durable companies understand gross margin before they pursue growth. The founders who do not usually discover the problem at the worst possible time.",
    author: "Nirmal Nambiar",
    date: "22-04-2026",
