          "The second advantage is contextual specificity. A small team can train an AI tool on its specific context  its brand voice, its customer base, its operational nuances  more completely than an enterprise can, because the context is smaller, more coherent, and held by fewer people. An AI assistant that knows everything about one brand's positioning, tone, and customer psychology is more useful than a generic enterprise AI tool deployed across a hundred brands with no specific context.",
