          "The total tool cost for covering these four functions adequately is under ₹15,000 per month. The time saving is typically 15-20 hours per week across the team. The output quality, when the tools are used with good inputs and appropriate review, matches or exceeds what a team twice the size would produce without AI. The competitive moat is not the tools  every competitor can access the same tools. It is the discipline of building AI workflows that actually run consistently, rather than using AI ad hoc when someone remembers to.",
